    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-heading">
        <h2>about</h2>
        <p>
          A design and build landscape firm creating indoor outdoor spaces tailored to each
          property and client.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="about-grid">
        <div>
          <p>
            Groundbreaking Landscapes is based in Marin County and specializes in custom designs
            and installations for many types of outdoor spaces. The focus is on turning existing
            properties into beautiful and useable living spaces that reflect the way people
            actually live.
          </p>
          <p>
            Client involvement is encouraged at every step. Planting palettes, stone, wood, and
            material choices are developed together so the finished landscape feels personal and
            cohesive. Each site is studied carefully, with attention to microclimate and the
            character of the architecture.
          </p>
          <p>
            The firm handles both design and construction, which keeps details aligned from the
            first sketch through final planting.
          </p>
        </div>
        <aside class="about-card">
          <h3>what we build</h3>
          <p>
            Full service landscape design and construction for Bay Area homes.
          </p>
